					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203527" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;" >DrChandra</a></span> <span class="odate time_1512273535 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">03 Dec 2017 03:58</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3644648">
									

<p>@A Random Day: I'm aware that site veterans generally frown on gratuitous links to 'classic' articles, since it's basically coat-tail riding and straight up uncreative, but I thought it made sense in-universe for Fuller to do it since he wants scips that are already famous to minimize his own workload.</p>
<p>While I'm posting I'll give a shout out to my beta readers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/goodeveningdrwhite" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2297355); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2297355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Goodeveningdrwhite" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2297355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/goodeveningdrwhite" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2297355); return false;">Goodeveningdrwhite</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;">Ihp</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3042342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="TheBillith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3042342)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;">TheBillith</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toastedraptor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2988260); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2988260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="toastedraptor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2988260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toastedraptor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2988260); return false;">toastedraptor</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2975899); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2975899&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Zachary Maxwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2975899)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2975899); return false;">Zachary Maxwell</a></span>.</p>
<p>The feedback I got was more varied than I usually get, so I guess this tale has a good deal of Your Millage May Vary.</p>

